Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Long live His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the next few decades,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,contentions rose as the eunuchs amassed more power.
