Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:34.64,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.991,411)}The Yellow Turban Rebellion
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Driven to the brink, the people could only rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless starving people rose high their flags, for one last, desperate push against fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally in the first month of\Nthe seventh year of Guānghé,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:44.35,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: January 184 AD
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the Yellow Turban Rebellion broke out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They burned local government buildings,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,murdered officials, and occupied cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,War quickly broke out throughout the empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Within ten days,\Nnews of the rebellion had spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The imperial court was stunned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:09.44,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,440,6260,10740)\pos(105,339)}Hé Jìn\NStyled: Suìgāo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, the Yellow Turbans are powerful, and the Imperial Army is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Permit the provinces to raise their own troops for defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:14.86,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(129.684,331)}Emperor Líng
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll leave it to you,\NGeneralissimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Appoint generals to levy troops\Nto suppress the rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Administrator Liú Yān of Yōu Province\Nhereby announces to the public:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"The Yellow Turbans have rebelled against His Majesty."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"They are now invading\Nthe lands of Yōu Province,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:08:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"causing harm and\Ncorrupting the common people."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"Local guardsmen are ill-prepared and inadequate to defend the province."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"With Heavens' mandate, His Majesty hath decreed:"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"Recruit strong and loyal\Nmen from all four corners"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"to reinforce the army\Nand protect the people."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:19.34,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(86.744,351)}Liú Bèi\NStyled: Xuándé
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:22.77,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(599.282,224)}Zhāng Fēi\NStyled: Yìdé
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a man, aren't you?\N The nation is in trouble, and all you do is sigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The market is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Butcher Zhāng?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Butcher Zhāng!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, coming, coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I'm sorry. I'm afraid you\Nwon't be able to eat meat today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re here, aren't you?\NCut me some meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I sell the meat\Nif my boss isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care. \NYou sell meat, I'll buy the meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the money, just give it!\NGo find Butcher Zhāng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare not disturb him,\N you go find him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so difficult about slaughtering a pig?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, this is your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why be afraid?\NJust sell the meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you sell it then.\NI can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The meat is in the well,\Nbut I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not just move the millstone aside?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead: Move the millstone then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know my boss\Npromised earlier that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,whoever can move this millstone, can keep the meat inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it and the meat is yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your boss going to lose his money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you can't move the millstone, then quit running your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the boss' business if there's money made or lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Good work, my friend! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, put it back in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir... powerful sir,\Nwhat will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the meat into small pieces.\NDistribute it to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Distribute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The meat belongs to me now.\NJust do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! I'll get right on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come one, everyone, get you some meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, this meat is on me. Take a piece, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go. Get me a piece. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You were here to buy meat\Nso you must pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If others can take\N some, why can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't take it anymore!\NPass me money, pass me money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay! Sir, here's your payment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's there, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fresh green beans, \Nwant to buy some?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What green beans?\NThis is clearly flour!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I sell fine products at a fair price.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing but flour!\NIt's nothing but flour!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you buying or milling?\NIf you're not buying, stop messing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You get mad over a couple of beans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you give away all my pork?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've come for a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one I want to hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:13.95,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I want to make a name for myself,\Nwouldn't these two men be good companions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's really extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:22.35,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This guy’s also a real man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You two heroes have excellent martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's admirable, really admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I heard you lifted the millstone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came here to see you myself,\Nthat's what I was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I thought you came\Ndemanding money for the pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That little piece of pork?\NNot worth mentioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don’t you two come to my place for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to rain.\NLet's take shelter at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Zhāng Fēi styled Yìdé!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:18.46,Header,,0,0,0,,Note: Style names are given upon reaching adulthood. They're used as a form of respect between\Npeople of the same generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I love making friends\Nwith heroes from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'm lucky to meet two new heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It really puts me in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,After you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come! After you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, bring wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Guān Yǔ, styled Yúnchǎng,\Nfrom Jiěliáng of Hédōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Liú Bèi, styled Xuándé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We three met by chance but feel familiar straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit. Sit. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've noticed you two are no ordinary men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently the Yellow Turbans are running rampant.\NThe realm is in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the time for heroes to rise. I wonder if you two heroes have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, back in Jiěliáng,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tolerate a local despot oppressing the locals,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so in a fit of anger, I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was forced to roam the jiānghú. It's been five or six years since the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:09.11,Header,,0,0,0,,Note: The martial arts sub-culture that exist\Non the fringes of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have many skills.\NI want to put them to use,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but in all my travels, I've found no opportunity to serve the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate that I haven't killed\Nall the villains in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the recruitment notice\Nat the city gate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to enlist in the army. It's my chance to test sword and destiny on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die on the battlefield,\NI will die as a true and valiant man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what a man ought to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll enlist with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?\NWill you enlist with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s with the long sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you implying that men\Nshouldn't help their country?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Right now, it is a time of chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}heroes emerge in troubled times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}For heroes such as you two, \Nit is the time to show your valor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}But why must you subject\Nyourselves to serve others?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}These times will create heroes,\Nand those heroes will influence the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Now the Yellow Turbans are in rebellion\Nand the world has responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}The court has ordered provinces to raise troops
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}because they are weak,\N with leaderless, feeble troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Also, the eunuchs continue to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Because of these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}there is bound to be\Nanother rebellion against tyranny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}When the Yellow Turban Rebellion is crushed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}the heroes of the times\Nwill surely rise up as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Which hero will be the one\Nto hold power under heaven then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}No one knows for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing your speech is worth more\Nthan ten years of books!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's admirable, really admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m just a pig butcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's\Nhappening in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You just tell me what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so hesitant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}There is a man who was\Noriginally a scion of the Hàn dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}His ancestor, Prince Jìng of Zhōngshān, was the 7th son of Emperor Xiàojǐng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}When his ancestor,\Nthe Marquis of Zhuōlù,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}failed to pay his annual\Ntribute to his ancestors,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}he was stripped of his rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}A branch of his family\Nheaded out to the countryside
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}and settled down in Lóusāng Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Lóusāng Village? I know of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}There's a thousand-year-old\Nmulberry tree there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}The tree is tall and crowned.\NHence the name, Lóusāng Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:22.15,Header,,0,0,0,,Note: Lóusāng literally means 'giant mulberry'
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}I also heard people saying\Nthe mulberry tree shelters a nobleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Yes, I'm familiar with this saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}However, for the last ten generations\N the descendants of this family
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}have been impoverished.\NThere's nothing but bare walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}As an imperial scion,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}why doesn't he restore\Nhis family's honor and rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}He began wandering at age 15, seeking teachers and making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}He often thought of serving the state\Nand championing the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}but now he's 28 and has achieved nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}In the end, all his\Naspirations will be spent in vain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}a heart full of tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the man before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say it earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That nobleman is right before me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Liú you say it,\Nand old Zhāng will do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to recruit local champions\Nand punish villains,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,only I don't have the resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to do something for the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I always speak the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A single thread cannot make a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A single tree doesn't make a forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm weak and can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't give up,\NI would gladly follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are like charcoal during a snowstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too generous of you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.06,0:23:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi pays his respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Liú,\Nyou don't have to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to achieve great deeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wandered about half my life
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.37,0:24:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,searching for like-minded\Npeople, until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After washing away the sand,\NI've finally discovered gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.82,0:24:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Destiny has brought us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to swear an oath of brotherhood\Nwith you two, sharing life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.26,0:24:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you two feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.06,0:24:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also thought of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.31,0:24:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as we three share heart \Nand mind, clay can be changed to gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.55,0:24:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, you have me with you,\Nand we'll accomplish great deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.88,0:24:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I'm just a fighter,\NI understand honor and loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.71,0:24:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As the adage goes,\N"a good bird chooses a good tree to perch on,"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.20,0:24:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"and a good man chooses\Na worthy lord to serve."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.33,0:24:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My life's wish is fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.08,0:24:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, my life is tied to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.86,0:25:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My flesh is your flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.20,0:25:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fully committed!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.73,0:25:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.44,0:25:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to go through thick and thin with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.84,0:25:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be your companion through life or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.64,0:25:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.24,0:25:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If my words are false,\Nmay heaven strike me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.95,0:25:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.75,0:25:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.82,0:25:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.77,0:25:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.44,0:25:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.75,0:25:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.93,0:25:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.56,0:25:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Although not born on the same day,\Nsame month or same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.80,0:25:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Although not born on the same day,\Nsame month or same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.02,0:25:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Although not born on the same day,\Nsame month or same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.00,0:25:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We seek to die on the same date,\Nsame month and same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.46,0:25:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We seek to die on the same date,\Nsame month and same year.
