Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.78,0:30:25.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(578.876,360.556)}Dǒng Zhuó\NStyled: Zhòngyǐng
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.07,0:30:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you running, rebel!?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.92,0:31:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Thank you, heroes, for saving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.97,0:31:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}I'll remember it for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.77,0:31:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}May I ask what positions\Nyou three currently hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.70,0:31:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}We are commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.80,0:31:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Commoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.50,0:32:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother, you can't just...?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.80,0:32:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.15,0:32:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother, don't bother Elder Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.77,0:32:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You achieved so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.37,0:32:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,yet were rewarded with a\Nlowly magistrate post in Ānxǐ county.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.70,0:32:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That Sūn Jiān just curried favor\Nwith the higher-ups and was made a major.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.07,0:32:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.27,0:32:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That stinking imperial court!\NIt deserves its rebellions!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.12,0:32:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother, watch your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.27,0:32:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a commander of \Nthe imperial court, don't be rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.25,0:32:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about that Dǒng Zhuó! He did nothing, yet received a good magistrate position!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.50,0:32:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By connecting with wealthy men
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.33,0:32:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and bribing the Ten Attendants,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.97,0:33:00.37,Header,,0,0,0,,Note: The Ten Attendants are the faction of eunuchs that control the Imperial Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.72,0:33:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That day on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.87,0:33:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,remember what he was like? \NTrying to flee like a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.94,0:33:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.65,0:33:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was up to me,\NI'd kill him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.00,0:33:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.74,0:33:34.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(130.387,264)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,4180,4540)}The County Supervisor
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.30,0:33:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the new magistrate of this county?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.50,0:33:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.00,0:33:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.02,0:33:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.10,0:33:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Liú Bèi?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.60,0:33:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your background?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.62,0:33:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm descended from Emperor Xiàojǐng\Nthrough Prince Jìng of Zhōngshān.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.40,0:33:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a scion of the Hàn dynasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.82,0:33:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.70,0:34:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me for lacking manners, my good sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.15,0:34:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.92,0:34:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're an imperial clansman,\Nplease do sit down, good sir. Let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.65,0:34:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.20,0:34:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.02,0:34:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're an imperial scion, may I ask
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.87,0:34:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you holding such a\Nlowly post as a county magistrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.15,0:34:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of my post, \NI'll do my best to help the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.75,0:34:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who recommended you to take this post, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.02,0:34:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I started recruiting within Zhuō commandery to suppress the Yellow Turbans.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.78,0:34:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been in more than thirty battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.90,0:34:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For my insignificant merits,\NI was rewarded with this post.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.02,0:34:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to find a big tree\Nto lean on in the court,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.90,0:34:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can lie low in the shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.52,0:35:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, it's fairly easy being a lowly official.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.00,0:35:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's harder for those higher on the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.02,0:35:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you want to do\N something, you need to pay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.82,0:35:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an honest official, I've never committed any offense against the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.40,0:35:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the slightest offense?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.90,0:35:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.85,0:35:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare not deceive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.87,0:35:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're so confident\N Magistrate Liú, I'd still like to check into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.05,0:36:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.82,0:36:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there any trouble, Elder Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.67,0:36:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.05,0:36:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.35,0:36:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't ask for a bribe?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.45,0:36:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not outright, but he was hinting at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.02,0:36:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I turned a deaf ear to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.97,0:36:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never exploit or mistreat the people. How could I afford to bribe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.22,0:36:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you had money, you shouldn't give it to him!\NWe'll see what he'll do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.87,0:36:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Magistrate Liú,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.15,0:36:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you're wanted by the Supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.07,0:36:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The Supervisoragain?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.30,0:36:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned bureaucrat, merely a bully\Nleaning on the powerful. Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.25,0:36:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Supervisor must be plotting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.77,0:36:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Best be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.45,0:37:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, the Supervisor\Nmust be harboring evil intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.22,0:37:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.77,0:37:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, Third Brother,\Nyou two wait for me at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.70,0:37:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.32,0:37:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.70,0:37:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.05,0:37:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.47,0:37:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your background?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.10,0:37:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm descended from Emperor Xiàojǐng through Prince Jìng of Zhōngshān.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.30,0:37:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Outrageous!\NYou dare pretend to be an imperial scion?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.10,0:37:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare pretend!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.17,0:37:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare answer back?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.02,0:37:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get this post,\Nhow much did you pay in bribes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.97,0:37:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Tell the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.37,0:37:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I started recruiting in Zhuō county to suppress the Yellow Turbans.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.06,0:37:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been in more than thirty battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.22,0:37:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For my insignificant merits,\NI was rewarded with this post.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.60,0:37:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you lie about your feats!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.42,0:37:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied about nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.37,0:37:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my duty to clean up\Ncorrupt officials like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.77,0:37:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.47,0:38:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave now. If I find any wrongdoing, you'll be sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.80,0:38:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I take my leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.70,0:38:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This Liú Bèi is so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.45,0:38:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Supervisor, as the saying goes,\N"a thief bites down to the bone."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.51,0:38:25.80,Header,,0,0,0,,Note: This saying means that bad people will be vindictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.40,0:38:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Supervisor announces\N a hearing in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.07,0:38:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,During these three days, anyone\Nwho is dissatisfied with the magistrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.20,0:38:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,has experienced injustice, corruption, or has any evidence of crimes done against the people
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.20,0:38:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,will be the first to be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.87,0:38:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Supervisor will protect you.\NYou don't have to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.90,0:38:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.50,0:38:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take revenge for the injustices done to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.92,0:38:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.45,0:39:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,since Magistrate Liú took office,\Nhe's committed no misdeeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.77,0:39:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He loves the common people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.72,0:39:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He has done no misdeeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.45,0:39:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.12,0:39:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he privately threaten you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.10,0:39:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that, absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.50,0:39:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorant peasants!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.12,0:39:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, the Supervisoris\Ndeliberately trying to frame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.90,0:39:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go beat him and run him\Nout of Ānxǐ county. It'll be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.40,0:39:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Third brother, don't be so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.91,0:39:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.40,0:39:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't beat him, can't even curse him!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.75,0:39:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.82,0:39:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.00,0:39:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.70,0:39:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.31,0:39:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.35,0:39:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.15,0:39:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.95,0:39:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.95,0:39:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.07,0:40:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going outside the city to ride my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.45,0:40:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.75,0:40:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but only outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.95,0:40:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.40,0:40:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Magistrate Liú, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.47,0:40:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Zhāng, the Supervisorhas been\Nintimidating us to turn against Lord Liú.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.66,0:40:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Zhāng, we went to petition on behalf of Lord Liú,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.02,0:40:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Supervisorwouldn't let us in\Nand he even beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.65,0:40:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.10,0:40:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.57,0:40:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You bureaucrat cur, where's my Elder Brother!?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.95,0:40:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You bureaucrat cur!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.25,0:40:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.13,0:41:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.58,0:41:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You cur! I should beat you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.12,0:41:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.72,0:41:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.97,0:41:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing this scumbag would be a good deed!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.33,0:41:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.02,0:41:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.40,0:41:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Supervisor, my Elder Brother\Nhas been nothing but dutiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.32,0:41:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's honest and cares for\Nthe people like his own children!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.65,0:41:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you try to harm him?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.35,0:41:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You only know how to steal money and ask for bribes!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.30,0:41:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly it's you who's the corrupt one!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.25,0:41:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My Elder Brother is innocent.\NWhere would he have the money for bribes?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.15,0:41:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}You sell positions and\Nconfiscate property on false charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.60,0:41:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}You deserve this punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.02,0:41:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé, sirs, sirs,\Nspare my life! Spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.07,0:41:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Elder Brother, you've achieved so much on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.88,0:41:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}yet only got to be a county magistrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.47,0:41:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}And now, you get slandered by this Supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.85,0:41:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}This place is a thorn bush,\Nnot fit for a phoenix to perch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.82,0:42:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Better to kill him, resign this post,\Nthen head out for a new opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.57,0:42:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me! I'll never do it again!\NThose above forced me into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.95,0:42:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Subordinates follow their superiors!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.30,0:42:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Supervisor! You tried to frame the honest\Nand you tried to harm the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.62,0:42:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserve to be put down like a dog,\N but I will spare you this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.25,0:42:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your favor, Lord Xuándé!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.80,0:42:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My post...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.97,0:42:37.12,Header,,0,0,0,,Note: Stamp seals represent government positions, and were required for decisions to be legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.45,0:42:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you may keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.42,0:42:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liú, please don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.47,0:42:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liú, please don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.20,0:43:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To avoid prosecution,\NLiú Bèi and his two brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.38,0:43:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,became captains under Liú Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.05,0:43:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After Gōngsūn Zàn mentioned Liú's previous achievements,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.06,0:43:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,he was promoted to major for the Píngyuán county magistrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.60,0:43:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There he gradually regrouped his old forces.
